Flask,

flask is a web gramework that provides libraries to build lightweight web applications in python. 
  developed by : Armin Ronacher who leads an international group of python enthusiasts(POCCO)
  based on : WSGI toolkit and jij=nja2 template engine,
  flas is considered as a micro framework

WSGI : web server gaeway interface is an interface between web servers and wed apps for python.  
  mod_wsgi is an Apache HPPT server module that enables apache to serve Flasks
